ncos.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebfn h\u00f4m nay, v\u1ecb vua \u00e1o \u0111en n\u00e0y ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u00f4ng gi\u1ecfi nh\u1ea5t &ndash; t\u1eb7ng th\u1ebb v\u00e0 trao nh\u1eefng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i cho Real Madrid. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Juve r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee9c th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 v\u1eady n\u1ebfu v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong hi\u1ec7p 1, tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Cuneyt Cakir \u0111\u00e3 cho Paulo Dybala 1 chi\u1ebfc th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng v\u00ec l\u1ed7i \u0103n v\u1ea1. Sang hi\u1ec7p 2, ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0 Dybala v\u1edbi l\u1ed7i cao ch\u00e2n, v\u00e0 1 chi\u1ebfc th\u1ebb n\u1eefa \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u00fat ra, khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y &ldquo;\u0111i t\u1eafm s\u1edbm&rdquo;. Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n x\u00e1c trong 2 pha th\u1ed5i ph\u1ea1t, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ecb vua s\u00e2n c\u1ecf n\u00e0o c\u0169ng s\u1ebd n\u01b0\u01a1ng tay cho Dybala \u1edf t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng th\u1ee9 hai, khi anh \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb th\u1ed5i ph\u1ea1t 1 l\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1eb7ng Ramos m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng trong hi\u1ec7p 2 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00f3n qu\u00e0 v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00f3 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Cuneyt Cakir, khi \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Real ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i v\u1edbi Dybala, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n b\u1ecb c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Argentina vung c\u00f9i ch\u1ecf v\u00e0o m\u1eb7t. Nh\u01b0ng \u1edf m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n, tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ed5 v\u1eabn cho Juve h\u01b0\u1edfng quy\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Trong tai Cuneyt Cakir uu ai Real o tran thang Juventus hinh anh\" title=\"Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Cuneyt Cakir \u01b0u \u00e1i Real \u1edf tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/4/Trong-tai-Cuneyt-Cakir-uu-ai-Real-o-tran-thang-Juventus-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ramos c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3m \u01a1n tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Cuneyt Cakir v\u00ec chi\u1ebfc th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng \u1edf t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd, Sergio Ramos s\u1ebd v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t trong tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m &ldquo;v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh&rdquo; b\u1ecb \u0103n th\u1ebb, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ebfn khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, Ramos c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3m \u01a1n Cakir v\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 &ldquo;v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh&rdquo; t\u1ea9y th\u1ebb gi\u00fap anh. Real Madrid coi nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, c\u00f2n Ramos &ldquo;\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c&rdquo; ngh\u1ec9 tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1, qua \u0111\u00f3 trong s\u1ea1ch \u1edf v\u00f2ng ti\u1ebfp theo.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 t\u1ec7&rdquo; &ndash; Ramos chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfc th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng oan \u1ee9c ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn. &ldquo;Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xem \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t khi t\u00f4i b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p, t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng trong khi t\u00f4i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1ed5i ph\u1ea1t sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Cuneyt Cakir d\u00e0nh cho Ramos, nh\u01b0ng sau t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, th\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00f3n qu\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb vua \u00e1o \u0111en t\u1eb7ng cho Real Madrid. V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda CLB Ho\u00e0ng gia, v\u1eeba xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u00e8 b\u1eb9p Juventus, v\u1eeba &ldquo;v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh&rdquo; nh\u1eadn qu\u00e0 c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ea7m c\u00e2n n\u00e0y m\u1ef1c, l\u00e0m g\u00ec c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0o thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i h\u01a1n th\u1ebf?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Juventus 0-3 Real Madrid</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/14088659/013100\" rel=\"nofollow\">Juventus vs Real Madrid<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</span>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/mot-tay-huy-diet-juventus-sieu-anh-hung-ronaldo-noi-gi-184-183484.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/4/mot-tay-huy-diet-juventus-sieu-anh-hung-ronaldo-noi-gi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/mot-tay-huy-diet-juventus-sieu-anh-hung-ronaldo-noi-gi-184-183484.html\">M\u1ed9t tay h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t Juventus, si\u00eau anh h\u00f9ng Ronaldo n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span><br>\r\nCristiano Ronaldo ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Juventus vs Real Madrid, anh h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u0103ng hoa tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Italia.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"778","checkdouble":"183487"},{"date":"08:04 04/04","title":"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Juventus vs Real: Khi \u201cMessi m\u1edbi\u201d qu\u00e1 nh\u1ecf b\u00e9 so v\u1edbi CR7","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/4/du-am-juventus-vs-real-khi-messi-moi-qua-nho-be-so-voi-cr7.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1px #888}.articlerelate:last-child{border-bottom:0}div.articlerelate>a{color:#000;te