='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1eefa Ronaldo v\u00e0 Dybala \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ebfn k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3&nbsp; tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Juventus vs Real Madrid.</strong></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n Ronaldo ng\u1eebng ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf Champions League</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng nay, Real Madrid c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Juventus trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch nh\u01b0ng Los Blancos ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng, h\u1ecd c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i h\u01a1n. K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng tri\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-0.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Du am Juventus vs Real Madrid  Messi moi qua nho be so voi CR7 hinh anh\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Juventus vs Real Madrid  Messi m\u1edbi qu\u00e1 nh\u1ecf b\u00e9 so v\u1edbi CR7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/4/mot-tay-huy-diet-juventus-sieu-anh-hung-ronaldo-noi-gi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ronaldo t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Juventus vs Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/ket-qua-juventus-vs-real-madrid-tran-dau-luot-di-tu-ket-champions-league-201718-184-183470.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u</strong></span> tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Italia mang l\u1ea1i l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf cho K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Zidane coi nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Juventus vs Real Madrid, si\u00eau sao Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o, CR7 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp uy hi\u1ebfp khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng x\u00e2m nh\u1eadp v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc Juventus, Ronaldo d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m 7 l\u1ea7n, 3 tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch, ngo\u00e0i ra anh c\u00f2n t\u1ea1o ra 2 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y trong c\u1ea3 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Juventus vs Real Madrid, Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. T\u1eeb \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u0103ng ngang c\u1ee7a Isco, CR7 b\u0103ng v\u00e0o d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea1m \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Buffon \u1edf c\u1ef1 ly g\u1ea7n. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0y cho th\u1ea5y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfm l\u0129nh kh\u00f4ng gian c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a Ronaldo. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng s\u1edbm nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a CR7 \u1edf Champions League (2 ph\u00fat 47 gi\u00e2y).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1edbi ph\u00fat 64, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/nhung-thong-ke-gay-soc-ve-ronaldo-o-tran-dau-voi-juventus-184-183475.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Ronaldo</strong></span> khi\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng C\u0110V c\u1ee7a Juventus ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady v\u1ed7 tay v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ng\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u00f3c b\u00f3ng v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p. Ch\u01b0a d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u1edf \u0111\u00f3, ph\u00fat 72 CR7 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 v\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o gi\u00fap Marcelo \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0. V\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1985 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0 C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"ronaldo\" title=\"ronaldo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/4/nhung-thong-ke-gay-soc-ve-ronaldo-o-tran-dau-voi-juventus.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Ronaldo l\u00e0 kh\u1eafc tinh c\u1ee7a Juventus</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nCristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 n\u00e2ng s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00ean con s\u1ed1 39, trong 5 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, kh\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi CR7 v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, d\u00f9 anh \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 32. C\u1ef1u sao MU l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Champions League ghi b\u00e0n trong 10 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 16 b\u00e0n. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, anh ghi b\u00e0n trong t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Champions League, v\u1edbi 14 b\u00e0n sau 9 tr\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Ronaldo l\u1eadp c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft gi\u00fap <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/real-madrid-29.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Real </strong></span>\u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Juventus 4-1, \u1edf l\u1ea7n t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y anh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin. CR7 cho th\u1ea5y anh l\u00e0 kh\u1eafc tinh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Italia. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, c\u1ef1u sao MU \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 9 b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Juventus \u1edf Champions League, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, Ronaldo ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n 10 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch \u0111\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 9 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. &ldquo;L\u00e3o phu nh\u00e2n&rdquo; c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Bayern Munich l\u00e0 hai CLB b\u1ecb c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi 9 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/cristiano-ronaldo-44953.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Ronaldo</strong></span> gi\u00fap Real c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 3 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng, 2 h\u00f2a v\u00e0 1 thua sau 6 l\u1ea7n gi\u00e1p m\u1eb7t Juventus. \u1ede tu\u1ed5i 32 CR7 v\u1eabn cho th\u1ea5y anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u0103ng hoa c\u1ee7a Ronaldo gi\u00fap Real chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 \u1edf Bernabeu.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Dybala qu\u00e1 nh\u1ecf b\u00e9 n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1eb7t c\u1ea1nh Ronaldo</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Ronaldo c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 th\u00ec Dybala, m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t b\u00ean ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. Trong hi\u1ec7p thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 c\u00f3 2 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Dybala gay that vong lon Juventus 0-3 Real Madrid\" title=\"Dybala g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn Juventus 0-3 Real Madrid\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/4/dybala.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Dybala ch\u01a1i m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nNgay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 9, Dybala \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a cho Juventus nh\u01b0ng anh l\u1ea1i d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m qu\u00e1 ch\u1eadm \u0111\u1ec3 Ramos k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1, sau \u0111\u00f3 anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng giao nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u1edf c\u1ef1 ly ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 20m, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfc ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1993 l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng \u0111i qua h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi m\u00e0 Juventus \u0111ang thua 0-2, h\u1ecd r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec hy v\u1ecdng l\u1eadt ng\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ebf c\u1edd \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 th\u00ec ch\u00ednh Dybala l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00f3ng l\u1ea1i c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda \u0111\u00f3. Chi\u1ebfc th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng th\u1ee9 2 \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y b\u1ecb tru\u1ea5t quy\u1ec1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf ph\u00fat 66, trong th\u1ebf 10 ch\u1ed1ng 11, Juventus kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n m\u00e0 c\u00f2n nh\u1eadn th\u00eam 1 b\u00e0n thua.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"dybala\" title=\"dybala\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/4/Nhung-diem-nhan-trong-tran-dai-chien-mot-chieu-Juventus-0-3-Real-hinh-anh-2.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Dybala kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c b\u1ecb \u0111u\u1ed5i kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n5 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t Dybala ghi 6 b\u00e0n, nh\u1eefng t\u01b0\u1edfng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Tottenham \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 v\u00f2ng 1/8 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c gi\u00fap &ldquo;Messi m\u1edbi&rdquo; thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5, nh\u01b0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real Madrid m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a anh ph\u1ea3i d\u00f9ng t\u1eeb th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda \u0111\u1ec3 mi\u00eau t\u1ea3. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng ph\u00fat c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y tung ra 4 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f4ng tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch, sau \u0111\u00f3 anh kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c b\u1ecb tru\u1ea5t quy\u1ec1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede tu\u1ed5i 25, Dybala m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 6 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i Champions League trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p, con s\u1ed1 b\u1eb1ng 1/3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch m\u00e0 Ronaldo th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e0y t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina v\u1eabn c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i ph\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a CR7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/nhung-diem-nhan-trong-tran-dai-chien-mot-chieu-juve-vs-real-184-183478.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Xem th\u00eam \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Juventus 0-3 Real Madrid<br>\r\n</strong></span><br>\r\n<strong>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 Juventus vs Real Madrid<br>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau Juventus 0-3 Real Madrid\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Juventus 0-3 Real Madrid\" src=\"https://static.bongd