ontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Italia ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch, \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Cris Ronaldo l\u1eadp si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Gianluigi Buffon.</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a anh \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i tr\u00ean to\u00e0n th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a Daniel Carvajal b\u00ean h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i, Ronaldo l\u1eadp si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m xe \u0111\u1ea1p ch\u1ed5ng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c, khi\u1ebfn Buffon \u0111\u1ee9ng nh\u01b0 tr\u1eddi tr\u1ed3ng.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a CR7, c\u00e1c C\u0110V Juventus \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i v\u1ed7 tay t\u00e1n th\u01b0\u1edfng ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c C\u0110V. C\u00f2n sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Gigi Buffon \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1 b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn, Ronaldo x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Maradona, hay Vua <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn\" title=\"bong da 24h\" type=\"bong da 24h\">b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span> Pele.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao khi n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Marcus Rashford:</strong> &ldquo;<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/cristiano-ronaldo-44953.html\" target=\"_blank\">Cristiano Ronaldo</span> l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00f9a. L\u00e0m sao anh \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady? M\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 phi th\u01b0\u1eddng!&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo l\u1eadp si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Juventus\" title=\"Ronaldo l\u1eadp si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Juve, c\u1ea3 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi c\u1ea1n l\u1eddi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/4/Ronaldo-lap-sieu-pham-vao-luoi-Juve,-ca-the-gioi-can-loi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ronaldo l\u1eadp si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Juventus</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Michael Owen:</strong> &ldquo;L\u1ea1y Ch\u00faa, n\u1ebfu Ng\u00e0i \u0111ang b\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay, h\u00e3y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Ng\u00e0i xem \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 2 c\u1ee7a Ronaldo. B\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7u c\u0169ng qu\u00e1 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, nh\u01b0ng n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n th\u1ee9 2 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd nh\u1ec9? <strong>Th\u00fa th\u1ef1c l\u00e0 t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng t\u00ecm ra l\u1eddi n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea3</strong>.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Rio Ferdinand:</strong> &ldquo;Ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c C\u0110V \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3. M\u1ed9t c\u00fa xe \u0111\u1ea1p ch\u1ed5ng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c qu\u00e1 tuy\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a Ronaldo!&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Trang ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/real-madrid-29.html\">Real Madrid</span>: </strong>&ldquo;\u0110\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o. Si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a Ronaldo l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ecbnh ngh\u0129a c\u1ee7a ngh\u1ec7 thu\u1eadt.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Trang ch\u1ee7 Champions League:</strong> &ldquo;119 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ghi b\u00e0n trong 10 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp. Cristiano Ronaldo l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, d\u00f9 t\u1ebfu t\u00e1o h\u1ea1 th\u1ea5p vi\u1ec7c Ronaldo l\u1eadp si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m khi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/zidane-noi-dieu-cuc-soc-ve-ban-thang-cua-cris-ronaldo-184-183480.html\" target=\"_blank\">cho r\u1eb1ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1eb9p h\u01a1n</span>, nh\u01b0ng ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a HLV Zidane \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 s\u1ef1 kinh ng\u1ea1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Phan ung cua Zidane trong tran Juventus vs Real Madrid\" title=\"Ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a Zidane trong tr\u1eadn Juventus vs Real Madrid\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/4/zida.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a Zidane trong pha ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n