0ng th\u1ee7. B\u1ecf qua c\u00fap Nh\u00e0 vua n\u01a1i th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean tung ra \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh 2, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 17 b\u00e0n sau 38 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i La Liga v\u00e0 Champions League m\u00f9a 2017/18 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00ednh ra, Barca ch\u1ec9 l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u00f3 0,44 b\u00e0n/ tr\u1eadn, con s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00e1ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1ea5y t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea1o. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Valverde, s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng c\u1ee7a Blaugrana lu\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1 cao v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u chuy\u00ean gia cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fac h\u1ecd s\u1edf h\u1eefu ph\u00f2ng tuy\u1ebfn v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barca vs Roma (1h45 ngay 54) Nghien hy vong thanh cat bui hinh anh\" title=\"Barca vs Roma (1h45 ng\u00e0y 54) Nghi\u1ec1n hy v\u1ecdng th\u00e0nh c\u00e1t b\u1ee5i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/4/Barca-vs-Roma-(1h45-ngay-54)-Nghien-hy-vong-thanh-cat-bui-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">H\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Barca l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111ang v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn gi\u1edd, Barca v\u1eabn \u0111ang b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf La Liga v\u00e0 Champions League, nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau t\u1ed1i th\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. Ch\u01b0a khi n\u00e0o c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1eady. Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real Madrid t\u1ea1i Si\u00eau c\u00fap T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh gi\u00fap \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Valverde nh\u1eadn ra h\u1ecd \u0111ang thi\u1ebfu nh\u1eefng g\u00ec.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 v\u00f2ng 1/8 l\u00e0 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a Barca m\u00f9a n\u00e0y. H\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 v\u1ed3 v\u1eadp c\u00f4ng ph\u00e1 khung th\u00e0nh b\u00ean kia, nh\u01b0ng c\u1ee9 khi n\u00e0o l\u00ean b\u00f3ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1ea1i run r\u1ea9y. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00f4m \u0111\u00f3, Chelsea c\u00f2n d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n (14 so v\u1edbi 8) song nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh nh\u1eadn v\u1ec1 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn thua 3 b\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng g\u1ee1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Messi giai cuu Barca\" title=\"Messi giai cuu Barca\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/1/Messi-giai-cuu-Barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Messi v\u1eabn l\u00e0 ngu\u1ed3n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng v\u00f4 t\u1eadn cho Blaugrana</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 kh\u00e1o nhau: H\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh l\u00e0m n\u00ean nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u cho m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Barca vs Roma, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Valverde t\u1ef1 tin r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 \u0111\u00f3. Barca s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1eb7p trung v\u1ec7 Gerard Pique v\u00e0 Samuel Umtiti ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t \u0103n \u00fd, trong khi Jordi Alba v\u00e0 Sergi Roberto l\u00e0 c\u1eb7p c\u00e1nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede gi\u1eefa s\u00e2n, nh\u1eefng Ivan Rakitic, Sergio Busquets v\u00e0 Paulinho b\u1ed5 sung cho nhau ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o. D\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Valverde, c\u1ea3 ba \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 ho\u1eb7c ch\u00ed \u00edt c\u0169ng l\u00e0 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u01b0 x\u01b0a. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 54 tu\u1ed5i lu\u00f4n \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi r\u1ea5t cao \u1edf c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/ernesto-valverde-cua-barca-tu-ke-ngoai-dao-den-nguoi-cua-so-menh-180-183065.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/29/ernesto-valverde-cua-barca-tu-ke-ngoai-dao-den-nguoi-cua-so-menh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/ernesto-valverde-cua-barca-tu-ke-ngoai-dao-den-nguoi-cua-so-menh-180-183065.html\">HLV Ernesto Valverde: T\u1eeb k\u1ebb ngo\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a s\u1ed1 m\u1ec7nh</span><br>\r\n<span>C\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Barcelona th\u1eddi Ernesto Valverde kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u00e0 ngo\u00e0i c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u1ea3m x\u00fac, Ernesto Valverde \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u cho...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n chuy\u1ec7n chia nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng cho 3 tuy\u1ebfn, c\u1ea3 t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 Barca gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i tu\u00e2n th\u1ee7 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i chung. Th\u1ebf m\u1edbi c\u00f3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh si\u00eau sao Lionel Messi kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng pressing g\u00e2y s\u1ee9c \u00e9p b\u00ean ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng th\u1ea5y tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Camp Nou.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t Barca c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi nay. C\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c, ghi m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Ter Stegen v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1. \u0110\u00e3 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 Real Madrid r\u1ea5t c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede ph\u00eda tr\u00ean, Messi \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 30 v\u1eabn l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n. Th\u00e0nh t\u00edch ghi 32 b\u00e0n, 14 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o sau 37 tr\u1eadn tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a Leo l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 ch\u1ee9ng th\u1ef1c r\u1ea5t thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c. Ch\u1eb3ng n\u00f3i \u0111\u00e2u xa, d\u00f9 c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, Messi v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c xoay chuy\u1ec3n th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn cho Barca tr\u01b0\u1edbc Sevilla.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barca an mung tran hoa Sevilla\" title=\"Barca an mung tran hoa Sevilla\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/1/Sevilla-vs-Barca-Nhiet-liet-hoan-ho-Valvelona-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Barca v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf l\u1ef1c t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Messi v\u00e0o s\u00e2n ph\u00fat 57, Barca b\u1ecb Sevilla l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt v\u1ec1 th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 may m\u1eafn m\u1edbi gi\u00fap h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2 b\u00e0n. Nh\u01b0ng trong th\u1eddi gian sau \u0111\u00f3, khi c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi 5 l\u1ea7n \u0111o\u1ea1t Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a Blaugrana \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y. Ngo\u00e0i mang t\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin cho c\u00e1c v\u1ec7 tinh xung quanh, ch\u00ednh Messi c\u00f2n l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 2-2 cho Barca.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1i c\u00e1ch m\u00e0 Barca ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Sevilla c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y h\u1eb3n c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn Roma n\u1ec3 s\u1ee3 ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o. \u0110i t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Italia v\u00e0 th\u1eadt ti\u1ebfc khi h\u1ecd g\u1eb7p ngay ph\u1ea3i Barca. Ngay t\u1eeb th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3, c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean Roma h\u1eb3n \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eafc \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u1ea7y qu\u1eady.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Barcelona vs Roma\" title=\"Preview Barcelona vs Roma\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/4/Preview-Barca-vs-Roma.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Barca vs Roma di\u1ec5n ra 1h45 ng\u00e0y 5/4</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nBarca vs Roma c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League. Nh\u01b0ng x\u00e9t phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Roma c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u01a1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha. C\u1ef1c ch\u1eb3ng \u0111\u00e3, tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Radja Nainggolan c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u00f2n d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00e0n so t\u00e0i th\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec9nh n\u00e0y v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u1ecf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p nhau g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Camp Nou, Barca \u0111\u00e8 b\u1eb9p Roma t\u1edbi 6-1 v\u1edbi hai ng\u00f4i sao Messi v\u00e0 Luis Suarez m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap. T\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t T\u00e2y Ban Nha r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng th\u1ee9 5 t\u1edbi, xem ra v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ch\u1ec9 n\u1eb1m \u1edf ch\u1ed7 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 th\u1eafng c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t bao nhi\u00eau b\u00e0n.&nbsp; <br>\r\n&nbsp;<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:<br>\r\nBarca (4-4-2): </strong>1.Stegen - 20.Roberto, 3.Pique, 23.Umtiti, 18.Alba - 11.Dembele, 15.Paulinho, 4.Rakitic, 8.Iniesta - 10.Messi, 9.Suarez.<br>\r\n<strong>Roma (4-3-3):</strong> 1.Alisson - 24.Florenzi, 44.Manolas, 20.Fazio, 11.Kolarov - 3.Pellegrini, 16.De Rossi, 6.Strootman - 17.Under, 9.Dzeko, 8.Perotti.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: Barca th\u1eafng 3-0<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Barcelona vs Roma\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Barcelona vs Roma\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/4/Barca-vs-Roma-(4-4-2-vs-4-3-3).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Barca vs Roma</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</strong><strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Barca vs Roma tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/day-chien-thuat-roma-vs-barca-tu-ket-c1-184-183448.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! Con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ng\u1eafn nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 Roma \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/monchi-phat-bieu-ve-barca-truoc-khi-doi-dau-roma-184-183397.html\">Ngo\u00e0i Messi, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 sao Barca ng\u01b0\u1eddi Roma s\u1ee3 nh\u1ea5t</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/barcelona-nhan-tin-cuc-vui-radja-nainggolan-cua-roma-chan-thuong-176-183237.html\">Barcelona nh\u1eadn tin c\u1ef1c vui t\u1eeb&hellip; \u0111\u1ea5t \u00dd</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/nguoi-y-khang-dinh-roma-khong-so-barca-184-183089.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Roma kh\u00f4ng s\u1ee3 Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/umtiti-noi-gi-truoc-tin-don-barca-quan-tam-griezmann-180-183457.html\">Umtiti n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n Barca quan t\u00e2m Griezmann?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div></b