\u00f9a.&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Liverpool th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o, Joel Matip ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00f9i trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 2-1 v\u1edbi Crystal Palace cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Selhurst Park (<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/video/tong-hop-crystal-palace-12-liverpool-vong-32-premier-league-201718-326-183239.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p Crystal Palace vs Liverpool</span></span>). Matip v\u1eabn ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ee7 90 ph\u00fat nh\u01b0ng trong cu\u1ed9c ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf sau tr\u1eadn, c\u00e1c b\u00e1c s\u0129 ch\u1ea9n \u0111o\u00e1n trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Cameroon ph\u1ea3i ph\u1eabu thu\u1eadt \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Joel Matip chan thuong nang, du kien nghi het mua.\" title=\"Joel Matip ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng, d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn ngh\u1ec9 h\u1ebft m\u00f9a.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/3/joel-matip-chan-thuong-nghi-het-mua-klopp-lo-sot-vo-ve-hang-thu.jpeg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Joel Matip ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng, d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn ngh\u1ec9 h\u1ebft m\u00f9a.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Matip ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft m\u00f9a, khi\u1ebfn HLV Jurgen Klopp c\u00f3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 e ng\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Liverpool. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Liverpool c\u0169ng \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Adam Lallana t\u00e1i ph\u00e1t ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 ngh\u1ec9 h\u1ebft m\u00f9a.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Jurgen Klopp n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c Joel Matip ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn Klopp th\u00eam \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/liverpool-vs-man-city-184-182215.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">Liverpool vs Man City</span></span> trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i Champions League 2017-18. Trong l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p nhau m\u00f9a n\u00e0y tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Anfield t\u1ea1i Premier League, Liverpool t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ec3 Man City ghi 3 b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Jurgen Klopp\" title=\"HLV Jurgen Klopp\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/2/HLV-Jurgen-Klopp.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Jurgen Klopp \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u sau khi Joel Matip ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00ec v\u1eady, HLV Jurgen Klopp kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y l\u1ea1c quan v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Joel Matip: &quot;T\u00f4i nh\u1eadn tin t\u1eeb hai h\u00f4m tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Sau tr\u1eadn, kh\u00f4ng ai ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y. Matip n\u00f3i c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u1ec9 \u0111au m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat v\u00e0 v\u1eabn ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng, th\u1ebf n\u00ean s\u1ebd \u1ed5n th\u00f4i&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec1u ngh\u0129 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p ch\u00e2n t\u00ea b\u1ea1i. \u0110i\u1ec1u duy nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 ch\u1eb3ng ai nh\u00ecn ra anh \u1ea5y \u0111ang b\u1ecb t\u00ea li\u1ec7t \u1edf ch\u00e2n. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00fat lo l\u1eafng. Tin t\u1ee9c n\u00e0y t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 t\u1ed3i, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Joe Gomez b\u1ecb \u0111au, Ragnar Klavan ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n v\u1ec1 s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe c\u00f2n Emre Can v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Matip s\u1ebd ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i v\u00e0 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tin t\u1ed1t duy nh\u1ea5t. Nh\u01b0ng n\u00f3 ch\u1eb3ng gi\u00fap ch\u00fang t\u00f4i nhi\u1ec1u trong th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i&quot;.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/truoc-tran-liverpool-vs-man-city-the-klopp-doa-huy-diet-doi-thu-184-183468.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/3/truoc-tran-liverpool-vs-man-city-the-klopp-doa-huy-diet-doi-thu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/truoc-tran-liverpool-vs-man-city-the-klopp-doa-huy-diet-doi-thu-184-183468.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Liverpool vs Man City, The Klopp d\u1ecda h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7</span><br>\r\nJurgen Klopp, Andrew Robertson hay Virgil Van Dijk \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111e d\u1ecda \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i Champions League 2017-18 gi\u1eefa Liverpool vs Man City.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"773","checkdouble":"183473"},{"date":"00:15 04/04","title":"Man Utd h\u1ea1 gi\u00e1 v\u00e9 nh\u1eb1m thu h\u00fat \"qu\u1ef7 tr\u1ebb\" \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e2n Old Trafford","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/3/man-utd-ha-gia-ve-nham-thu-hut-quy-tre-den-san-old-trafford.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1px #888}.articlerelate:last-child{border-bottom:0}div.articlerelate>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.articlerelate>a:hover{color:#f00;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}.articler