0ean tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb m\u00f9a sau nh\u1eb1m chi\u1ec1u theo y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Jose Mourinho.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n, Jose Mourinho \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u00e1c <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mourinho-co-dong-vien-man-utd-nhiet-thanh-hon-chelsea-172-155063.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean Man Utd</span></span> &quot;nhi\u1ec7t&quot; h\u01a1n n\u1eefa, t\u1ea1o n\u00ean b\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed n\u00e1o nhi\u1ec7t h\u01a1n n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00edch l\u1ec7 tinh th\u1ea7n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. Nh\u1eb1m th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n theo \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0y, Man Utd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u01a1 c\u1ea5u l\u1ea1i gi\u00e1 v\u00e9 trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018-19.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Man Utd ha gia ve voi cac co dong vien tre tuoi.\" title=\"Man Utd h\u1ea1 gi\u00e1 v\u00e9 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/3/man-utd-ha-gia-ve-nham-thu-hut-quy-tre-den-san-old-trafford.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Man Utd h\u1ea1 gi\u00e1 v\u00e9 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Man Utd h\u1ea1 gi\u00e1 v\u00e9 cho c\u00e1c c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean tr\u1ebb (18-25 tu\u1ed5i) xu\u1ed1ng c\u00f2n 15 b\u1ea3ng, t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng 21 USD cho m\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i Stretford End. Ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o CLB hy v\u1ecdng vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e2n s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed s\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Richard Arnold, Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh Man Utd chia s\u1ebb: &quot;Vi\u1ec7c c\u01a1 c\u1ea5u l\u1ea1i gi\u00e1 v\u00e9 cho nh\u00f3m c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean tr\u1ebb thu\u1ed9c di\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c nh\u00f3m trong di\u1ec5n \u0111\u00e0n c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9, m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u00e0 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>K\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 2018 c\u1ee7a Man Utd</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trang ch\u1ee7 c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 c\u0169ng th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o v\u1ec1 tour du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 2018 v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0 Hoa K\u1ef3. Chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn k\u00e9o d\u00e0i trong hai tu\u1ea7n, v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean g\u1eb7p Club America (Mexico) t\u1ea1i SV\u0110 \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Phoenix (Glendale, Arizona) v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 19/7.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Man Utd nam thu hai lien tiep du dau he tai My.\" title=\"Man Utd n\u0103m th\u1ee9 hai li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/4/mu-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Man Utd n\u0103m th\u1ee9 hai li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn ng\u00e0y 22/2, Man Utd s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n San Jose Earthquakes, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i nh\u00e0 ngh\u1ec1 M\u1ef9 (MLS) tr\u00ean SV\u0110 Levi (Santa Clara). C\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i trong tour du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 2018 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt t\u1eeb gi\u1edd cho \u0111\u1ebfn cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a tr\u00ean trang ch\u1ee7 c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00f3 Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch, Ed Woodward chia s\u1ebb: &quot;Chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e0 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e2m trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch k\u00e9o d\u00e0i \u1edf c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9 cao. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 n\u0103m th\u1ee9 hai li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ebfn M\u1ef9. C\u01a1 s\u1edf t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e1m \u0111\u00f4ng c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean cu\u1ed3ng nhi\u1ec7t, t\u1ea1o m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi&quot;.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cau-hoi-man-utd-bo-nhiem-mourinho-de-lam-gi-172-182951.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/21/cau-hoi-man-utd-bo-nhiem-mourinho-de-lam-gi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cau-hoi-man-utd-bo-nhiem-mourinho-de-lam-gi-172-182951.html\">C\u00e2u h\u1ecfi: Man Utd b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Mourinho \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m g\u00ec?</span><br>\r\nS\u00e1u n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, quan \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Sir Bobby Charlton v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi k\u1ebf nhi\u1ec7m Sir Alex Ferguson \u1edf Old Trafford ch\u1eb3ng kh\u00e1c g\u00ec g\u00e1o n\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1ea1nh d\u1ed9i v\u00e0o l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Jose...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"772","checkdouble":"183474"},{"date":"16:54 03/04","title":"CLB FLC Thanh H\u00f3a b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u0129nh \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a L\u0110B\u0110 ch\u00e2u \u00c1","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/3/thanh-hoa-bat-ngo-linh-an-phat-cua-ldbd-chau-a.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;mar