ges/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1eb1ng kinh nghi\u1ec7m trong ngh\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 thao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, BLV k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u V\u0169 Quang Huy \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1eb1ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch t\u1eadp \u0111o\u00e0n truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Thanh Ni\u00ean, Nguy\u1ec5n C\u00f4ng Kh\u1ebf l\u00e0 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch VFF.</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i ban ch\u1ea5p h\u00e0nh (BCH) VFF kh\u00f3a 8 di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 4 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd ch\u1ecdn ra nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t m\u1edbi v\u00e0o c\u00e1c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch v\u00e0 ph\u00f3 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch. Sau khi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-viet-nam/bau-duc-phan-phao-manh-me-sau-tam-thu-dai-dong-cua-ong-tran-anh-tu-168-182586.html\" target=\"_blank\">b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i \u00f4ng Tr\u1ea7n Anh T\u00fa</span> v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed Ph\u00f3 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch VFF ph\u1ee5 tr\u00e1ch t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i VFF l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a NHM.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ong Nguyen Cong Khe, Truong Ban TVDD buc xuc truoc cach lam viec tho o cua BTC giai.\" title=\"\u00d4ng Nguy\u1ec5n C\u00f4ng Kh\u1ebf, Tr\u01b0\u1edfng Ban TV\u0110\u0110 b\u1ee9c x\u00fac tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1ch l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c th\u1edd \u01a1 c\u1ee7a BTC gi\u1ea3i.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2013/8/DSC-0019n-1376625787_500x0-2013816124251.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>BLV Quang Huy \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 \u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n C\u00f4ng Kh\u1ebf ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch VFF</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed quy\u1ec1n l\u1ef1c nh\u1ea5t VFF - ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch VFF kh\u00f3a 8, ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean tri\u1ec3n v\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 Ph\u00f3 Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch th\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u1ef1c VFF Tr\u1ea7n Qu\u1ed1c Tu\u1ea5n hay Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c Khu Li\u00ean h\u1ee3p th\u1ec3 thao qu\u1ed1c gia M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh, \u00f4ng C\u1ea5n V\u0103n Ngh\u0129a.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean theo nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a BLV Quang Huy, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ea7m n\u1eafm gi\u1eef ch\u1ee9c v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a VFF trong s\u1ed1 c\u00e1c \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean Ph\u00f3 Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch VPF Nguy\u1ec5n C\u00f4ng Kh\u1ebf, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch t\u1eadp \u0111o\u00e0n truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Thanh Ni\u00ean - \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c nhi\u1ec1u gi\u1ea3i U17, U19, U21 trong th\u1eddi gian qua.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cTheo quan \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y \u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n C\u00f4ng Kh\u1ebf l\u00e0m Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch VFF l\u00e0 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n c\u1ea3, b\u1edfi \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u \u00f4ng Kh\u1ebf c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi VFF trong vai tr\u00f2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1ebb. \u00d4ng Kh\u1ebf c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ch\u1ecbu nh\u1eefng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f2n v\u1edbi anh Tr\u1ea7n Qu\u1ed1c Tu\u1ea5n, c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 trao \u0111\u1ed5i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi anh \u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng, t\u00f4i t\u1ef1 th\u1ea5y anh Tu\u1ea5n \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m Ph\u00f3 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch ph\u1ee5 tr\u00e1ch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n s\u1ebd ph\u00e1t huy \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. D\u00f9 sao anh Tu\u1ea5n c\u0169ng c\u00f2n tr\u1ebb, c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u1edf ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc\u201d, BLV Quang Huy chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean VTC News.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb BLV nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0i n\u00e0y c\u0169ng nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 VFF c\u1ea7n t\u00ecm ra ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ea7m v\u00e0 b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u1ed3i v\u00e0o gh\u1ebf Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch v\u00e0 Ph\u00f3 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch ph\u1ee5 tr\u00e1ch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n. C\u00f2n c\u00e1c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed kh\u00e1c th\u00ec ai \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1edbn.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thanh Long (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bau-duc-noi-khong-voi-viec-tro-thanh-chu-tich-vff-168-183358.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/23/bau-duc-noi-khong-voi-viec-tro-thanh-chu-tich-vff.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bau-duc-noi-khong-voi-viec-tro-thanh-chu-tich-vff-168-183358.html\">B\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch VFF</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eed v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch VFF kh\u00f3a 8, v\u1ecb ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"768","checkdouble":"183460"},{"date":"20:40 03/04","title":"HLV Park Hang Seo l\u00ean danh s\u00e1ch 58 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam cho Asiad 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/24/hlv-park-hang-seo-len-danh-sach-58-cau-thu-u23-viet-nam-cho-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatep