  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp v\u1edbi VFF, HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 danh s\u00e1ch 58 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho Asiad 2018.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u00e1ng nay (3/4), Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam (VFF) \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 bu\u1ed5i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi HLV Park Hang Seo v\u1ec1 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. Hai tr\u1ecdng t\u00e2m ch\u00ednh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho Asiad c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 AFF Cup 2018 - gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-viet-nam-la-hat-giong-so-1-aff-cup-2018-168-181124.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">\u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 h\u1ea1t gi\u1ed1ng s\u1ed1 1</span></span>.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Park Hang Seo\" title=\"HLV Park Hang Seo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/24/hlv-park-hang-seo-len-danh-sach-58-cau-thu-u23-viet-nam-cho-asiad-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Park Hang Seo l\u00ean danh s\u00e1ch 58 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho Asiad 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd l\u00e0 HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 <strong>danh s\u00e1ch 58 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</strong> \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho Asiad 2018. Theo d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 23/7 n\u00ean th\u1ea7y Park cho bi\u1ebft ch\u01b0a c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 b\u1ea3n danh s\u00e1ch n\u00e0y, m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch l\u00e0 theo d\u00f5i c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u00eam tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Kh\u00f4ng ai ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y nh\u1eafc nh\u1edf c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eeba tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, thay v\u00ec nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ngo\u00e0i chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y b\u1ecb e ng\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c ph\u00e2n t\u00e2m khi ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3ng qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 tham d\u1ef1 nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u1eddi nh\u1eafc nh\u1edf \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f9ng vi\u1ec7c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh s\u00e1ch 58 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 d\u1ee5ng \u00fd c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park, nh\u1eb1m c\u1ea3nh t\u1ec9nh c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u01a1n v\u00ec ch\u1eb3ng ai ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-viet-nam/cac-tuyen-thu-u23-viet-nam-se-tham-du-asiad-2018-vao-khi-nao-168-178880.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018</span></span> d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1eeb 14/8 \u0111\u1ebfn 1/9. Th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m v\u1eeba l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u00e1p l\u1ef1c v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo. B\u1edfi nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u00fd th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00fang v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p s\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, VFF c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb th\u1ea7y Park \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch AFF Cup 2018, theo k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch di\u1ec5n ra t\u1eeb 5/11 \u0111\u1ebfn 15/12/2018. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft, HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 s\u1ebd d\u1ef1 kh\u00e1n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-le-thuy-hai-du-doan-tran-dai-chien-u23-cua-ha-noi-vs-hagl-168-183452.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs HAGL</span></span> v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 5/4 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 m\u1edbi cho U23 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/vleague/cong-phuong-quang-hai-chua-ghi-ban-la-chuyen-binh-thuong-291-183431.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/13/cong-phuong-quang-hai-chua-ghi-ban-la-chuyen-binh-thuong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span