ecda \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i Champions League 2017-18 gi\u1eefa Liverpool vs Man City.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/truc-tiep-boc-tham-tu-ket-cup-c1champions-league-201718-18h00-ngay-163-372-182183.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m Champions League 2017-18</span></span> khi\u1ebfn hai \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u00f2n s\u00f3t l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh l\u00e0 Man City ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n nhau \u1edf v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. M\u00f9a n\u00e0y, hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n nhau m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Anfield v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c 4-3 d\u00e0nh cho The Klopp.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mohamed Salah la niem hy vong so mot cua The Kop truoc tran Liverpool vs Man City.\" title=\"Mohamed Salah l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a The Kop tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Liverpool vs Man City.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/3/truoc-tran-liverpool-vs-man-city-the-klopp-doa-huy-diet-doi-thu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Mohamed Salah l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a The Kop tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Liverpool vs Man City.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y ti\u1ebfp th\u00eam s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Jurgen Klopp tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i gi\u1eefa Liverpool vs Man City v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam 5/4 (theo gi\u1edd Vi\u1ec7t Nam). C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n s\u1ebd bung h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c khi Man City s\u1eafp l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League, c\u00f2n Liverpool c\u0169ng b\u1ecf xa Chelsea trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00e0o top 4.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>The Klopp tuy\u00ean chi\u1ebfn</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u Man City kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf l\u00e0 v\u1eady&quot; - Jurgen Klopp t\u1ef1 tin tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 tr\u00ean trang ch\u1ee7 UEFA: &quot;C\u00e1ch ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu. N\u1ebfu ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t, Man City s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean khi h\u1ecd t\u1ea1o ra ma thu\u1eadt t\u1eeb hai c\u00e1nh. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n ph\u1ea3i d\u00e8 ch\u1eebng c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i khi h\u1ecd c\u00f3 b\u00f3ng \u1edf c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd c\u1ea3nh ph\u1ea3i khi b\u00f3ng xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u1edf bi\u00ean \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n b\u00ean tr\u00e1i. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u01b0ng th\u1eadt kh\u00f4ng may, h\u1ecd lu\u00f4n tri\u1ec3n khai b\u00f3ng \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao nh\u1ea5t, t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng di\u1ec5n ra v\u1edbi nh\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ed9 nhanh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt cao. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f2n v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Jurgen Klopp\" title=\"HLV Jurgen Klopp\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/2/HLV-Jurgen-Klopp.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Jurgen Klopp \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Man City trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra e ng\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng Andrew Robertson kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd khai th\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong tr\u1eadn Liverpool vs Man City: &quot;Kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n Man City th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y&quot;.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n h\u1ecd t\u1ea1i Anfield v\u00e0i th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ed9 ra nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu, b\u1eb1ng ch\u1ee9ng l\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ba b\u00e0n trong 10 ph\u00fat. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu khi ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ba b\u00e0n. Hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng, th\u1ebf l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 khi \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i v\u00e0 v\u1ec1&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Virgil Van Dijk th\u00ec l\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/mane-tin-tuong-salah-se-vui-dap-man-city-184-183401.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">Mohamed Salah</span></span> \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111e d\u1ecda \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7: &quot;Anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c l\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. Khi \u1edf phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t, anh \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. C\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n Salah nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, b\u1edfi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 m\u1ea5t&quot;.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/khong-bat-ngo-neu-liverpool-ha-man-city-de-vao-ban-ket-c1-172-183447.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/3/khong-bat-ngo-neu-liverpool-ha-man-city-de-vao-ban-ket-c1.PNG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/khong-bat-ngo-neu-liverpool-ha-man-city-de-vao-ban-ket-c1-172-183447.html\">Kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u1ebfu Liverpool h\u1ea1 Man City \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft C1</span><br>\r\nNh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Liverpool vs Man City \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i Champions League, c\u1ef1u sao tuy\u1ec3n Anh David James \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 The Kop cao h\u01a1n Man xanh.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"762","checkdouble":"183468"},{"date":"17:09 03/04","title":"H\u00e9 l\u1ed9 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n Higuain ph\u1ea3i \u201cb\u00e1n x\u1edbi\u201d kh\u1ecfi Real","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/3/cha-higuain-phat-bi