37.html\">Barca</span> nh\u1eafm mua Marquinhos l\u00e0m ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf.</strong></h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y tr\u00ean <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/tin-chuyen-nhuong-c187-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span>, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p &ndash; <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/tu-choi-cam-ket-voi-barca-umtiti-se-sang-man-united-172-182867.html\">Umtiti r\u1eddi Barca</span> l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ch\u1ecbu gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n v\u00ec \u0111\u00f2i t\u0103ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp, trong khi gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a anh ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u euro.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do Barca nh\u1eafm mua Marquinhos &ndash; trung v\u1ec7 Brazil \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho PSG. Hi\u1ec7n nay, Man United l\u00e0 CLB s\u1ed1t s\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t trong vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Umtiti, v\u00e0 Barca c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng trong m\u1ecdi ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n, b\u1edfi h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n r\u01a1i v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng m\u1ea5t ng\u01b0\u1eddi r\u1ed3i m\u1edbi mua, d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u1ecb \u00e9p gi\u00e1 nh\u01b0 \u1edf m\u00f9a h\u00e8 v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t, Barca \u0111\u00e3 theo \u0111u\u1ed5i trung v\u1ec7 Marquinhos t\u1eeb l\u00e2u, khi anh c\u00f2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho AS Roma v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2013. V\u00e0 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd, G\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 x\u1ee9 Catalonia s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ng\u00e0y n\u00e0o c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barca nh\u1eafm mua Marquinhos th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 Umtiti\" title=\"Barca nh\u1eafm mua Marquinhos th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 Umtiti\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/3/maquinhos.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca nh\u1eafm mua Marquinhos th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 Umtiti</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/psg-104.html\">PSG</span> hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, CLB n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Cup qu\u1ed1c gia Ph\u00e1p, v\u00e0 \u0111ang \u0111\u1ebfm ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111em Ligue 1 v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0, nh\u01b0ng n\u1ed9i t\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a PSG l\u1ea1i r\u1ea5t ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Julian Draxler \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng khai ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch HLV Unai Emery, trong khi Thomas Meunier &ldquo;l\u1ee1 mi\u1ec7ng&rdquo; ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ebd ra \u0111i s\u1edbm.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1edfi v\u1eady, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi cho nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ea1i gia kh\u00e1c v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c, \u0111\u01a1n c\u1eed l\u00e0 Barca trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 &ldquo;h\u1eadu qu\u1ea3&rdquo; khi h\u1ecd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ecfi mua tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p. M\u00f9a h\u00e8 tr\u01b0\u1edbc, h\u1ecd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111em v\u1ec1 Verratti nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i c\u00f2n b\u1ecb PSG cu\u1ed7m m\u1ea5t Neymar.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, n\u1ebfu th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Barca nh\u1eafm mua <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/marcos-aoas-correa-44608.html\">Marquinhos</span> kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c, HLV Ernesto Valverde ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n sang nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c d\u1ec5 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 h\u01a1n. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 Matthijs de Ligt v\u00e0 Cl\u00e9ment Lenglet, ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n nh\u1ea5t, chi ti\u1ec1n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho Umtiti.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/umtiti-noi-gi-truoc-tin-don-barca-quan-tam-griezmann-180-183457.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/3/umtiti-noi-gi-truoc-tin-don-barca-quan-tam-griezmann.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/umtiti-noi-gi-truoc-tin-don-barca-quan-tam-griezmann-180-183457.html\">Umtiti n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n Barca quan t\u00e2m Griezmann?</span><br>\r\nTrung v\u1ec7 Samuel Umtiti \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n Antoine Griezmann t\u1edbi Barca \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"760","checkdouble":"183456"}]}